  "text": "Remifentanil dosage for LMA in elderly few as one-fifth the numbers (only 23 patients) of patients as the traditional design with a preset number of patients at each level [CITATION_1] . This means that we could minimize the number of patients given insufficient treatment. However, ED 95 could not be obtained with probit analysis because adequate number of remifentanil concentration was not used in this study. We assumed that the ED 95 of remifentanil is < 0.3 μg/kg because all six patients given 0.3 μg/kg remifentanil had excellent LMA insertion but the number of patients seems to be inadequate to make a conclusion.",
